    innovation:"Where causal logic optimises means to achieve a fixed goal, effectual logic generates goals from available means. Where standard frameworks emphasise prediction, effectuation emphasises control and co-creation. Where causal logic minimises risk via expected return, effectual logic caps downside via affordable loss.",
