    byWhom:"Marketing managers, product managers, finance teams allocating capacity, and corporate strategy teams managing portfolios.",
    innovation:"Vernon extended what was then a marketing concept into international economics, linking the product's lifecycle to migration of production. Compared to Rogers' Diffusion of Innovations (which focuses on adopters), the PLC focuses on the producer's economics across phases.",
