    byWhom:"Marketers, public-health officials, change-management leaders, technology adoption consultants, and policymakers.",
    innovation:"Where prior diffusion models focused on individual psychology, Rogers built the theory on social-system characteristics and communication channels. The five adopter categories and five adoption attributes have been empirically validated across more domains than perhaps any other social-science framework.",
