    byWhom:"Strategy consultants, investment analysts, MBA students, corporate strategy teams, and competition-policy regulators.",
    innovation:"Compared with the SWOT tradition (which mixed internal and external factors), the Five Forces isolated industry structure as the primary determinant of profit. Compared with later resource-based and dynamic capabilities views, Five Forces remains the dominant lens for industry attractiveness.",
