    innovation:"Compared with Porter's generic strategies (cost leadership vs differentiation as a binary choice), Blue Ocean Strategy claims the two can be combined via value-curve reconstruction. Compared with feature-list innovation, the Four Actions Grid mandates explicit elimination — the action most strategists avoid.",
    figureCaption:"A 2×2 grid with quadrants labelled Eliminate / Reduce / Raise / Create, surrounding a value-curve graph with old curve dotted and new curve solid showing the resulting reshape.",
