    byWhom:"Strategy academics, executive teams, strategy consultants, MBA educators, and family-business advisors.",
    innovation:"Compared with Porter's positioning-centric view, Mintzberg's 5 Ps acknowledged that 'strategy' as practised was multi-dimensional. Compared with planning-centric views, the inclusion of Pattern (emergent strategy) was particularly influential.",
