    byWhom:"Corporate strategy directors, divisional general managers, M&A advisors, private-equity portfolio managers, and consultants.",
    innovation:"Compared with single-business strategic frameworks, the BCG Matrix introduced explicit cross-business resource allocation. Compared with later portfolio frameworks (GE Matrix, Three Horizons), BCG's two-axis simplicity remains its enduring strength and limitation.",
