    whoDeveloped:"Daniel Goleman (b. 1946), psychologist and former New York Times science writer, popularised EI in Emotional Intelligence (1995). Goleman drew on the academic work of Peter Salovey and John Mayer (1990), then refined the four-quadrant model with Richard Boyatzis and Annie McKee in Primal Leadership (2002).",
