    innovation:"Compared with stage-based growth models, Adizes' lifecycle is bidirectional — firms can move backward (toward Prime) as well as forward (toward Aristocracy). Compared with Greiner's curve (F49), Adizes is more diagnostic-rich and more useful for mature/declining firms specifically.",
